{"tid":2065040,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請湯家驊答11條問題 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-06-15T08:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T09:08:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1934a8471ded858e5cac146f969b8e6f3e80edb6","tid":2065040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200615/20937411/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200615%2F20937411%2F&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7gDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=85103c3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200615%2F20937411%2F&h=484f0b4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200615/20937411/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n請湯家驊答11條問題 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200615/large/1592128601_cef6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200615%2Flarge%2F1592128601_cef6.jpg&h=512b063e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nnow新聞截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n資深大狀湯家驊最近出席論壇，就國安法這個熱門話題，講了一番令我獲益良多的偉論，只是有些不明白的地方，希望向湯大狀討教：<br />\n<br />\n1、你說近日與北京官員對話，對方保證香港的檢控權、獨立終審權等在立法後不會改變，請問你傳達這個黨八股「保證」，是想安撫、說服，抑或惹怒香港人？<br />\n<br />\n2、京官有三個口，。。。。。。。。。。們承認會「改變」呢？<br />\n<br />\n3、近一年，無數市民被律政司濫控，警察犯罪證據確鑿，律政司卻視若無睹，甚至有警察的家屬販毒，也可撤控，所謂「香港的檢控權不變」，湯大狀是否認為香港人很希罕？<br />\n<br />\n4、你說香港法律本。。。。。。。。。。什麼反對第23條立法？<br />\n<br />\n5、查2002年11月12日政府公報，當時的署理保安局常任秘書長湯顯明談過這叛國罪，說《刑事罪行條例》已有數十年歷史，為第23條立法時，必須「更新及改善《刑事罪行條例》中有關叛國的條文」，「把有關罪行定義收窄」。從前政府不引用叛國罪，不是不敢，而是認為條例不當，湯大狀是否認為現存的叛國罪沒問題？<br />\n<br />\n6、2003年香港政府。。。。。。。。。。。覺得香港已倒退為不必再講人權的社會？<br />\n<br />\n7、你說國安法是藤條，但只有藤條教不好小朋友，同時要有波板糖，期望日後有柔和政策，讓香港人二次回歸。喂阿哥，官方說法係國安法只針對「少數人」，佢係藤條定坦克，關大多數人咩事先？你現在說什麼「香港人二次回歸」，我好驚喎。<br />\n<br />\n8、香港人。。。。。。。。。「小朋友」？<br />\n<br />\n9、小朋友不喜歡波板糖又如何？<br />\n<br />\n10、香港人是小朋友，。。。。。。。。。。。，抑或金魚佬？<br />\n<br />\n11、你為什麼滿腦子都是小朋友？ <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 undefinedhilomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"06b1e2255aa83f4f172a5faecb9ff7607c7fb439","tid":2065040,"uid":207247,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"你為什麼滿腦子都是小朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ace92cf6d3a8406593a6956c13eca9323e3c1f","tid":2065040,"uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"點解要問11條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e04fd23d9b344a377a5a8a2028965ef3143fead","tid":2065040,"uid":191633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:59:35.000Z","msg":"答第11條就夠"},{"pid":"2b153f0adcf601746ea63589f6575f962cc88a62","tid":2065040,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06b1e2255aa83f4f172a5faecb9ff7607c7fb439","tid":2065040,"uid":207247,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"你為什麼滿腦子都是小朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.civicparty.hk/sites/default/files/1234.gif?1374484544\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.civicparty.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F1234.gif%3F1374484544&h=2dc86da4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5f8d4df7e314ed4e1277039db39ce4b52e9e312","tid":2065040,"uid":207247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b153f0adcf601746ea63589f657