020-06-15T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"肥仔OMDB"},{"pid":"b83ba5df81eab87a815e87489765112cd4036edc","tid":2065040,"uid":297152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"十一哥對小朋友有特殊偏好，一手波板糖，一手藤條，用嚟同小朋友玩遊戲。"},{"pid":"9eaefbecc5bd09b35c2ad127676814c4ebfa9b7c","tid":2065040,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}